n FP is kind of interesting.  I've played this game for a while now and can run through all the non-moon zones blindfolded.  But I am still learning.  Learning about people.  Learning about how they work together.  Learning about what to do when they can't work together.<br><br>There are times when I wish FP was more ubar.  There are times when all I want is to go off and solo with my alts.  But the times when we come together, I am reminded how nice it is to have a close family.  That is how it feels.  Yea, I know alot of people talk about their guild as a family, but often I think its a clique.  Its a close group of friends who play together in the same time zone.  <br><br>FP is 'different'.  Yea, we have a core of people who live near and play together alot.  But I have made friends, DEAR friends with people across this country now.  Friends who I would seriously consider joining whatever new guild they left ours for.  I look for them on ICQ or IM to chat about life and the game, even when I can't be in the game. <br><br>The daily grind of day to day EQ playing can sometimes make us forget how dear we are to each other in our guild.  Just one grouping with people in LiLo reminds me very quickly of how great the people are in my guild.<br><br>SO....<br><br>Give us a tell in game or post here.  <br><br>We are looking for people who:<br><br>Realize the game is just that; a game.<br><br>Understand that even though its just a game, there are real, feeling people behind the toons.<br><br>Value friendship and harmony over loot or coin.<br><br>Are willing to learn how we do things.<br><br>Are willing to teach us, patiently, how they do things.<br><br>Appreciates the beauty that can be achieved through compromise, patience, and dedication.<br><br>And finally, Knows deep in their heart that the most important part of any relationship is the 'relationship,' not the members of that relationship.<br><br>Look for us in game.<br><br>You'll find us together, I am sure.<br><br>Zantoz<br><br> <p>______<BR>zantoz<BR>Honor is more than a word.<BR>AKA: Stizi, Jaqulain, Zackreferin, Crezix, Sazant</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br><a href=http://pub92.ezboard.com/fmystiquessoulfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=17.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub92.ezboard.com/fmystiquessoulfrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=17.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub92.ezboard.com/fmystiquessoulfrm15.threadControl?topicID=17.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub92.ezboard.com/fmystiquessoulfrm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=17.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub92.ezboard.com/fmystiquessoulfrm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=17.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub92.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="mystiquessoulfrm1">The Gathering of Voices<option value="mystiquessoulfrm20">Fate's Presence Chat Room<option value="mystiquessoulfrm3">Friends and Family (Keeping Tabs on Eachother)<option value="mystiquessoulfrm5">Upcoming Events<option value="mystiquessoulfrm14">Adventures, Humor, and Other Fun Stuff<option value="mystiquessoulfrm15">Recruitment for